*   Code Academy资源：http://www.codecademy.com/tracks/javascript
*   Marjin Haverbekex编写的_Eloquent JavaScript_：http://eloquentjavascript.net/
*   John Resig编写的_Advanced JavaScript_：http://ejohn.org/apps/learn/

